# SHOPKEEPER MODULE ARCHITECTURE

Last Update: 04.03.2026

---

# Core Modules

System built with modular service architecture.

Each module contains:

Repository
Service
Domain Logic

---

# Modules

## Retail Module

Purpose:

Retail marketplace listings.

Components:

RetailRepository
RetailService

Functions:

createRetailProduct()
publishProduct()

Status:

Stable

---

## Order Module

Purpose:

Order lifecycle management.

Components:

OrderRepository
OrderService

Functions:

createOrder()
confirmOrder()

Order lifecycle:

created
confirmed
funds_frozen
completed

Status:

Stable (Phase 1)

---

## Ledger Module

Purpose:

Financial accounting system.

Components:

LedgerService

Functions:

freezeFunds()
releaseFunds()

Ledger structure:

Wallet
LedgerEntry

Status:

Working

---

## Wallet Module

Purpose:

User balances.

Components:

Wallet table

Functions:

balance management
fund transfers

Status:

Working

---

## Audit Module

Purpose:

Immutable system history.

Components:

AuditRepository

Events:

PRODUCT_PUBLISHED
ORDER_CREATED
ORDER_CONFIRMED_FUNDS_FROZEN

Status:

Active

---

# Infrastructure Layer

Components:

Prisma Client
Database
Migration system

Architecture:

Singleton Prisma instance
Repository abstraction

Status:

Stable

---

